2b00a32cc6708fcd0cfe54d5b4895f64f8295044fdfa1c5e7adcddb630fe6cb3564330a9ebd6b801e7469befc45a26f48aa18620f3b7cf5a27272d54cda442c0  0001-remove-rpath.patch"
